{
  "stem": "11144.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how many people traveled-- on the roof, on the-- I mean, it was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I by myself went to Radom because I found out also from my aunt that my aunt survived in Radom.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I wanted very much-- I remembered her as a single woman who used to take me on her dates, and who bought me my first ice skates.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I was very attached to her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And having somebody, you know, that survived, I had to see her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all by myself, I went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It took me one night to get back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It took me one day to be in Radom and one day-- a whole day to get back to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I made it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you find her?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I found her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We spent one day, and I went back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at that time, when we got to Lodz, we found from my aunt that everybody was killed because they knew-- they knew everything, whatever.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because my aunt was-- I think my aunt was on Polish papers, too, but I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My aunt might have been in a camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my cousins were-- one of my cousins was saved in Warsaw under a Polish name, and worked as a Polish maid.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So from them, we found out about the concentration camps, and found out about the families, and found out who-- you know, that everybody was killed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We also found out that my uncle, who lived later in Paris, went to Auschwitz and that he survived.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So-- and from the books, because all of a sudden, I started reading like-- like a mad-- like a madperson about these concentration camps, and about the horrors, and about the thing.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at that time, we found out everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
